Detailed Description

template<typename PTYPE>
class muscle::ConduitEntranceSingle< PTYPE >

complementary class for the Java muscle.core.JNIConduitEntrance using single primitive type data, e.g.

muscle.core.JNIConduitEntrance<java.lang.Double, Object>
use muscle::ConduitEntranceArray to access arrays of primitive data instead of single values
note: though java.lang.Double is an object, the muscle::ConduitEntranceSingle will yield a jdouble, not a jobject access an entrance which yields single primitive datatypes (send)

Author:
Jan Hegewald
